task.summary: For demo/POC - service for getting data from Norwegian authorities based on car reg no + service for importing vehicle data (in progress) + service for fetching data with GraphQL (in progress)

Further work on Vehicle import: - If the same data is imported multiple times, it will generate a new version of the same objects (not new objects) - DeckPlan will be connected to the VehicleType in the database - References from Vehicle, VehicleType and VehicleModel are handled so that the references to the correct objects are stored in the database - PassengerCapacity is saved
